name: Cuadro #2
description:
This image is based on the famous painting known as Girl With A Pearl Earring (Het meisje met de parel, 1665-1667) from Johannes Vermeer.

Cuadro #2 is part of a collection.

It was generated algorithmically with Python and Pillow. 150,000 pixels were randomly taken. Each of these pixels expands to form a 300-pixel straight line in a random direction. The width of each line is 1, 2 or 3 pixels, value selected at random with weights of 8, 2 and 1 respectively.

With this technique a textile texture or something similar is achieved.

Size: 4578 x 5216 px.
